The following [[Outline (list)|outline]] is provided as an overview of and topical guide to management:

'''[[Business management]]''' &ndash; [[management]] of a [[business]]. It includes all aspects of overseeing and supervising business operations. Management is the act of allocating resources to accomplish desired goals and objectives efficiently and effectively; it comprises planning, organizing, staffing, leading or directing, and controlling an organization (a group of one or more people or entities) or effort for the purpose of accomplishing a goal.

{{TOC limit|limit=2}}

