* [[Strategic planning]] &ndash; 
** [[Business plan]] &ndash; 
*** [[Business process]] &ndash; 
*** [[Business Process Modeling]] &ndash; (BPM) activity of representing processes of an enterprise, so that the current ("as is") process may be analyzed and improved in future ("to be").

