=== Persons influential in business management ===

* Pioneers of management methods
** [[Jack Welch]] &ndash; implemented [[six sigma]] throughout General Electric, leading to its widespread adoption throughout industry.
** [[Stafford Beer]] &ndash; introduced [[management cybernetics]] to British steel industry and was responsible for the first use of computers in management.
* [[List of business theorists|Business theorists]] &ndash; 
** [[C. West Churchman]] &ndash; 
** [[Peter Drucker]] &ndash; 
