|width="340"|{{legend|#E65959|Both ages unsynchronised: School leaving age higher / Employment age lower}} || '''0''' denotes education is not compulsory. '''(13)''' denotes part-time employment available from 13
|-
|width="340"|{{legend|#F4EA66|Both ages unsynchronised: Employment age higher / School leaving age lower}} || '''0''' denotes no minimum employment age as children could be, in theory, employed from birth
